"{\"uid\": \"thesouthafrican.com-lifestyle-celeb-news-local-celebs-illuminati-ban-long-jump-luvo-manyonga-how-blew-r84million-drugs-olympic-medal-crystal-meth\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Copyright Blue Sky Publications (Pty) Ltd. All Rights Reserved.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 63, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 15, \"end\": 18, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sky_UK\", \"score\": 0.557512185381609, \"rank\": 0.7689917426076724, \"text\": \"Sky\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sky_UK\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sky_UK\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"thesouthafrican.com is a division of Blue Sky Publications Ltd. Reproduction without permission prohibited  Home\\u00bb'They called us the Illuminati': Banned long jumper Luvo Manyonga on how he blew R84m  'We would blow R300 000 in two days on drugs': Troubled Olympic silver medallist Luvo Manyonga opens up about how he lost it all.\", \"from\": 65, \"to\": 394, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 107, \"end\": 110, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sky_UK\", \"score\": 0.557512185381609, \"rank\": 0.7689917426076724, \"text\": \"Sky\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sky_UK\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sky_UK\"}, {\"begin\": 198, \"end\": 208, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Illuminati\", \"score\": 0.9739050410390337, \"rank\": 0.026794148310103006, \"text\": \"Illuminati\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Illuminati\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Illuminati\"}, {\"begin\": 230, \"end\": 243, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Luvo_Manyonga\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Luvo Manyonga\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Luvo_Manyonga\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Luvo_Manyonga\"}, {\"begin\": 346, \"end\": 359, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Luvo_Manyonga\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Luvo Manyonga\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Luvo_Manyonga\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Luvo_Manyonga\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"EveryI Blew Itstory has a common denominator or more - they are cars, alcohol and women.\", \"from\": 396, \"to\": 484, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 403, \"end\": 407, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Blew\", \"score\": 0.9999999856213436, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Blew\", \"types\": [\"Q482994\", \"Q386724\", \"Q2188189\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Blew\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Blew\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"However, every so often, drug addiction also rears its ugly head and plays a major role in someone's downfall.\", \"from\": 485, \"to\": 595, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"For Luvo Manyonga, an Olympic long jump silver medallist, his addiction to crystal meth saw him lose it all.\", \"from\": 596, \"to\": 704, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 600, \"end\": 613, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Luvo_Manyonga\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Luvo Manyonga\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Luvo_Manyonga\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Luvo_Manyonga\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The 33-year-old athlete - who is also the African long jump record holder - opened up on theMzansi Magic documentary seriesabout how he blew R84 million in a couple of years  I Blew Itlooks into the lives of South Africans who struck gold when they received an unexpected good fortune, but blew it all in an instant.\", \"from\": 706, \"to\": 1022, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Manyonga's life changed for the better after his endorsement deals with Nike in 2017 and 2018, which saw him pocketing an astounding R84 million.\", \"from\": 1024, \"to\": 1169, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1096, \"end\": 1100, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Project_Nike\", \"score\": 0.99729025844793, \"rank\": 0.002712782001710163, \"text\": \"Nike\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Project_Nike\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Project_Nike\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"These came after he had been suspended in 2012 when crystal meth was detected in his urine.\", \"from\": 1170, \"to\": 1261, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1222, \"end\": 1234, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Methamphetamine\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"crystal meth\", \"types\": [\"Q8386\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Methamphetamine\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Methamphetamine\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"They suspended me for 18 months.\", \"from\": 1263, \"to\": 1296, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"After the ban, I continued using drugs, and things started going South.\", \"from\": 1297, \"to\": 1368, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I was smoking, robbing people until 2015,\\\" Manyonga explained.\", \"from\": 1369, \"to\": 1431, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"That year he relocated to Pretoria to train for the Rio de Janeiro Olympics which were held in Brazil in 2016.\", \"from\": 1433, \"to\": 1543, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1459, \"end\": 1467, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pretoria\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.0960843353012733e-16, \"text\": \"Pretoria\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pretoria\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pretoria\"}, {\"begin\": 1485, \"end\": 1499, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rio_de_Janeiro\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 7.218767672500202e-20, \"text\": \"Rio de Janeiro\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\", \"Q3957\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rio_de_Janeiro\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rio_de_Janeiro\"}, {\"begin\": 1528, \"end\": 1534, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brazil_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.93215403723663, \"rank\": 0.07267609467636098, \"text\": \"Brazil\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brazil_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brazil_national_football_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"During that tournament, Manyonga won a silver medal.\", \"from\": 1544, \"to\": 1596, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"The country gave me R250 000 and in 2017 I got a big deal from Nike for R42 million\\u2026 In 2018 also, plus minus the same amount,\\\" he said.\", \"from\": 1598, \"to\": 1735, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1662, \"end\": 1666, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Project_Nike\", \"score\": 0.99729025844793, \"rank\": 0.002712782001710163, \"text\": \"Nike\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Project_Nike\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Project_Nike\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Manyonga spent his money on expensive cars, women and drugs.\", \"from\": 1737, \"to\": 1797, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"That was after he renovated his parents' house in Paarl, Western Cape, and took care of his family and some of his community members' needs.\", \"from\": 1798, \"to\": 1938, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1848, \"end\": 1853, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paarl\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.3354130964288833e-27, \"text\": \"Paarl\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paarl\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paarl\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"The cars I rented cost R20 000 per day.\", \"from\": 1940, \"to\": 1980, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"On top of that I'd pay R100 000 for insurance because I'd return them wrecked the next day.\", \"from\": 1981, \"to\": 2072, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I would hide my drugs between the car seats and struggle to get them out and tear the seat\\u2026 in three days, I'd burst the car tyres.\\\"\", \"from\": 2074, \"to\": 2207, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Manyonga also bought luxury German cars.\", \"from\": 2209, \"to\": 2249, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2237, \"end\": 2243, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Germany\", \"score\": 0.5681651823037495, \"rank\": 0.7190702371417725, \"text\": \"German\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Germany\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Germany\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I bought the German Coupe for roughly R900 000\\u2026 Also, I'd be renting presidential hotels,\\\" he added.\", \"from\": 2251, \"to\": 2352, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2265, \"end\": 2271, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Germany\", \"score\": 0.5681651823037495, \"rank\": 0.7190702371417725, \"text\": \"German\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Germany\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Germany\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"According to his best friend and uncle, Sphelele Kwaza, they spent close to R400 000 on accommodation at a hotel for a month - where they partied up a storm.\", \"from\": 2354, \"to\": 2511, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2403, \"end\": 2408, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kwaza_people\", \"score\": 0.9877697501228253, \"rank\": 0.012381680928856704, \"text\": \"Kwaza\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kwaza_people\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kwaza_people\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"His sister, Vuyiseka Manyonga, added that the athlete had his own personal drug dealer.\", \"from\": 2512, \"to\": 2599, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We were daredevils.\", \"from\": 2601, \"to\": 2621, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"We were called the Illuminati,\\\" Kwaza said.\", \"from\": 2622, \"to\": 2665, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2641, \"end\": 2651, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Illuminati\", \"score\": 0.9739050410390337, \"rank\": 0.026794148310103006, \"text\": \"Illuminati\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Illuminati\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Illuminati\"}, {\"begin\": 2654, \"end\": 2659, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kwaza_people\", \"score\": 0.9877697501228253, \"rank\": 0.012381680928856704, \"text\": \"Kwaza\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kwaza_people\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kwaza_people\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"They called him Lucifer.\", \"from\": 2666, \"to\": 2691, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2683, \"end\": 2690, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Devil\", \"score\": 0.9781857118890898, \"rank\": 0.02025704102299138, \"text\": \"Lucifer\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Devil\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Devil\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I was Hellboy.\", \"from\": 2692, \"to\": 2706, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2698, \"end\": 2705, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hellboy\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 9.541962342570432e-33, \"text\": \"Hellboy\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hellboy\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hellboy\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"We were the Illuminati in Gqeberha\\u2026 We would blow R300 000 in two days on drugs,\\\" he added.\", \"from\": 2707, \"to\": 2798, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2733, \"end\": 2741, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Port_Elizabeth\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Gqeberha\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Port_Elizabeth\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Port_Elizabeth\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In 2021,SowetanLIVEreported that Manyonga had been banned for four years for a doping violation.\", \"from\": 2800, \"to\": 2896, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Manyonga was accused of missing an out-of-competition drug test on 26 November 2019 and then two filing failures, on 1 April 2020 and 1 October 2020, where he failed to properly submit his whereabouts for upcoming months.\", \"from\": 2898, \"to\": 3119, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Speaking onI Blew It, he said his agent had failed to give an update on his home address, which is why he missed the tests.\", \"from\": 3121, \"to\": 3244, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"With the athlete down and out and hooked on drugs, he was sent to a rehabilitation centre in Durban but escaped.\", \"from\": 3246, \"to\": 3358, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3339, \"end\": 3345, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Durban\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.98467500848533e-25, \"text\": \"Durban\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Durban\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Durban\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He ended up living in an abandoned building in the KwaZulu-Natal city.\", \"from\": 3359, \"to\": 3429, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3410, \"end\": 3423, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/KwaZulu-Natal\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.4212805589633635e-26, \"text\": \"KwaZulu-Natal\", \"types\": [\"Q3455524\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/KwaZulu-Natal\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/KwaZulu-Natal\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Manyonga is hoping to get a new lease in life when his ban ends in December this year  'The South African' is hiring!\", \"from\": 3431, \"to\": 3548, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Freelance writer positions available.\", \"from\": 3549, \"to\": 3586, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Send us your CV  Today's Daily Lotto jackpot stands at an estimated R400 000.\", \"from\": 3587, \"to\": 3664, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3600, \"end\": 3602, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Curriculum_vitae\", \"score\": 0.9999196410310773, \"rank\": 7.384708212623717e-05, \"text\": \"CV\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Curriculum_vitae\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Curriculum_vitae\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"If you want to win your share of the jackpot, you have to play!\", \"from\": 3665, \"to\": 3728, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Take a look at what the weather has in store for South Africa's nine provinces this Tuesday, 9 December 2025.\", \"from\": 3730, \"to\": 3839, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3779, \"end\": 3791, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Africa\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.879707308723488e-14, \"text\": \"South Africa\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Africa\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Africa\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Every FIFA World Cup 2026 match will have a three-minute pause in the middle of each half - effectively splitting the game into quarters.\", \"from\": 3841, \"to\": 3978, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"These are the three stadiums at which Bafana Bafana will play their three Group A FIFA World Cup 2026 matches.\", \"from\": 3980, \"to\": 4090, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4018, \"end\": 4031, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Africa_national_soccer_team\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Bafana Bafana\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Africa_national_soccer_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Africa_national_soccer_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"WSAR teams were called out to Cecelia Forest after a hiker reported an unconscious and unresponsive man near the waterfall.\", \"from\": 4092, \"to\": 4215, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Mamelodi Sundowns have reportedly signed a prolific teenage striker who many believe is Mzansi's very own 'Haaland'.\", \"from\": 4217, \"to\": 4333, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"TheSouthAfrican.com is all about South Africa and the stories that affect South Africans, wherever they are in the world.